column5:
Hi, 

I would like to buy a massage for my sister Tomorow Canese. She lives in Paia. I read reviews about your massage and I really think she will love it. I was thinking to buy her the 80$ massage. Can you please let me know how this works before I make the purchase online? Or should I call you and pay over the phone? Let me know! Thank you very much.

Best regards,

Marena Canese
